(WOMAN CHATTERING IN ITALIAN)

563
00:39:06,594 --> 00:39:08,678
-Benetti.
-What?

564
00:39:08,763 --> 00:39:10,847
-Rewind it.
-I can't rewind it.

565
00:39:10,931 --> 00:39:13,350
