at an awkward moment.

996
01:17:58,006 --> 01:17:59,715
Please forgive me.

997
01:18:00,300 --> 01:18:01,842
See you around.

998
01:18:04,096 --> 01:18:05,596
An old friend.

999
01:18:07,474 --> 01:18:08,933
(GRUNTING)

1000
01:18:10,268 --> 01:18:11,727
Okay, hold on.

1001
01:18:13,605 --> 01:18:14,939
