01:19:29,931 --> 01:19:31,682
(SPEAKING ITALIAN)

1013
01:19:40,233 --> 01:19:41,525
(PANTING)

1014
01:19:49,493 --> 01:19:51,535
(SIREN WAILING)

1015
01:20:10,222 --> 01:20:16,894
Carlo!

1016
01:20:17,437 --> 01:20:18,854
LECTER: Yes?

1017
01:20:19,481 --> 01:20:20,981
Good evening.

1018
01:20:31,368 --> 01:20:32,910
(BLOOD GURGLING)

1019
