1021
01:21:38,018 --> 01:21:39,476
or hello?

1022
01:21:41,646 --> 01:21:43,439
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

1023
01:21:55,035 --> 01:21:56,869
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)

1024
01:22:11,718 --> 01:22:13,177
(PANTING)

1025
01:22:25,273 --> 01:22:27,149
